uch that I am sending cash out of my pockets. I am conent to let them get their few cents every time I visit.  My experience, however, has always been that those that put the least into something will complain the most when it is gone, so if something does happen, I fully expect most of the folks blocking all ads to be the ones the most upset about the service demise. I am just sayin, if ya don't wanna contribute in one of the ways possible, don't complain when we no longer have the service.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ukalledar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalledar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 168<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/30/01 11:49:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2209.topic&index=42>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ...</span><hr size=1> See that? Aktunka made a well thought argument, he disagrees with me and yet he did not resort to insults and derogatory comments. Something to be learned here... <p><B><I><FONT FACE="verdana"><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="880020">Ji<FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="770560">ng</FONT><BR>60 Or<FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="770560">ac</FONT><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="700980">le </FONT><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="661290">of</FONT><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="6115a0"> Dr</FONT><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="5519c1">in</FONT><FONT SIZE="2" COLOR="4824d8">al</FONT></FONT><BR></B></I><BR>
